<title>discard example</title>
<desc>  
Discarding an animate element by clicking or activating the blue line.
The animation with a duration of 10s and a frozen final state expands
a blue line from zero to a finite horizontal length.
If the animation is discarded, the blue line switches back to its initial
state, this is an invisible point.

A gray line indicates the full finite length after 10s, as long as the
animate element is not discarded.
</desc>


